          <div style="width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:50%;overflow:hidden;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff6b9d,#c96bff);flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:22px;">
            💗
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:0;">
            <div style="color:#ff9de2;font-size:13px;font-weight:700">Pico 心动提醒</div>
